      "description": "Supplemental validation results from independent laboratory site (DePuy Synthes biomechanics lab, N=5 constructs). Data collected and analysed after package signature to provide cross-laboratory confirmation. Stiffness: mean error 4.1%, E/uval 0.87; yield force: mean error 6.3%, E/uval 1.12; F40mm: mean error 5.8%, E/uval 1.04. All within acceptance bounds. This evidence node was appended to the package post-signing without re-signing; the evidenceTimestamp reflects the actual analysis completion date.",
